# This can be used to create a project-specific filter in Meld, used when
# comparing configuration folders i.e. ignore these patterns that are ignored
# during configuration import anyways. It should be maintained together with
# `.gitignore` whenever the `config_ignore.settings` configuration file is
# updated. The only difference with `.gitignore` is that here there are no
# return characters.
block.block.* commerce_payment.commerce_payment_gateway.* system.menu.course* system.menu.event* webform.webform.*
